# API Design Workshop - API Tester agent

NAME api-tester

INPUT task

GOAL test """
Write an integration test suite for the API:
- Happy path for each endpoint
- Error cases (bad input, not found, conflict)
- Edge cases (empty body, large payload, concurrent requests)
- Auth tests (missing token, expired, wrong role)
- Pagination boundary tests
Use Go's net/http/httptest. Tests must be runnable with go test.
Output ONLY the test code.
""" -> test_suite

RUN main USING test
